data.revised_prompt: Create a professional, high-quality image of a 'Vodka Sunset Elixir' cocktail. This cocktail boasts a striking gradient of colors that flow from a deep red at the base to a captivating sunny orange shade, courtesy of the grenadine and fresh orange juice respectively. The cocktail is elegantly presented in a sleek, curved highball glass and adorned with a thin lime wheel and an elderflower blossom. This vibrant drink is set against a soothing, subtly blurred sunset backdrop which complements the tropical allure of the cocktail. The ambient lighting gently emphasizes the reflective texture of the glass, casting delicate patterns on the smooth wooden surface beneath. The image should be clear and in a soft-focus, photorealistic style, devoid of any text or watermarks.
